        # DemocracyOS, what is this?
        
        [DemocracyOS](http://democracyos.org) is an [Open Source Platform](https://github.com/democracyos) to argue, debate and vote on specific political issues, at a time when the internet has changed almost every aspects of everyday life, except for democracies. 
        
        Invented in 2012 by Argentinian developers and political scientists, the software is now being freely replicated all over the world. 
    
